---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#5b4bd9] via-[#6C5CE7] to-[#8a7cf0] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

            <div>
                <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img src="/images/logo-liderazap-br.png" alt="LideraZap"
                         class="h-12 w-auto" />
                </a>
                <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80 max-w-sm">
                    Gestão de redes sociais, vídeos para negócios e presença online feita por especialistas. Simples, direto e com resultado de verdade.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Navegação</h4>
                <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
                    <li><a href="#servicos" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition">Serviços</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#sobre" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition">Sobre</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contato" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition">Contato</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Conecte-se</h4>
                <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-4">
                    <a href="#" class="p-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-[#6C5CE7] transition">
                        <span class="icon-[mdi--instagram] text-[22px]"></span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="p-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-[#6C5CE7] transition">
                        <span class="icon-[mdi--facebook] text-[22px]"></span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="p-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-[#6C5CE7] transition">
                        <span class="icon-[mdi--youtube] text-[24px]"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/20 pt-6 text-center text-sm text-white/70">
            &copy; {year} <span class="font-semibold">LideraZap</span>. Todos os direitos reservados.
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>